Wanzor, Appellant, v. Wanzor, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.)

Argued before Labbemobe, C. J., and Daly and Van Hoesen, JJ.

B. Estes, for appellant. Hascall, Clarke & Vanderpoel, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with costs. For former report, see 5 N. V. Supp. 957.
